name.k: BeReal. Tes amis pour de vrai.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: For its millions of users, seeing and being seen on BeReal is a comfort. Its photo-only feed gives an authentic glimpse of what the people you care about most are experiencing as they go about their day. The apps simplicity reintroduces what feels like a novel idea: a realistic glimpse into what your friends are doing, seeing, and experiencing.
The simple photo-only feed gives an authentic glimpse into the lives of what friends and loved ones are doing, seeing and experiencing.
